HC12T8 – Merge Two Sorted Lists

Main.hs
mergeLists :: [Int] -> [Int] -> [Int]
mergeLists [] ys = ys
mergeLists xs [] = xs
mergeLists (x:xs) (y:ys)
    | x <= y    = x : mergeLists xs (y:ys)
    | otherwise = y : mergeLists (x:xs) ys
main :: IO ()
main = print (mergeLists [1,3,5] [2,4,6])

HC12T9 – Read and Print File Content
Write a program that reads a file and prints its content to the terminal. Handle errors gracefully in case the file doesn't exist.
Main.hs
readFileSafe :: Bool -> String
readFileSafe exists =
    if exists
        then "File content goes here"
        else "Error: File not found"
main :: IO ()
main = putStrLn (readFileSafe True)

